# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PRIVATE-BY-DEFAULT
# Nothing in this repo is tracked unless explicitly allow-listed below.
# To promote a file/folder to shareable: place it under shared/, or add
# a `!` un-ignore rule here. Be deliberate — anything tracked becomes
# visible to the design team when this repo is shared.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Ignore everything by default.
*

# 2. Keep these meta files visible.
!.gitignore
!README.md

# 3. Shareable zone — anything placed here is tracked.
!shared/
!shared/**

# 4. OS / editor noise — stays ignored even inside shared/.
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
